	<h2>Why we publish these guides</h2>
	<p>
		Good nutrition information is often either too vague to act on or buried in jargon. We write practical,
		evidence-based guides on nutrition, weight management, GLP-1 medications, protein, and healthy habits — the
		same topics our app helps people with every day. The goal is simple: clear advice you can actually use.
	</p>

	<h2>How these articles are written and reviewed</h2>
	<p>
		Every article is researched against current, mainstream nutrition science and written in plain English by the
		Nutrify AI team, then reviewed for accuracy before publishing. We avoid hype, fad claims, and absolute
		promises. Where a topic touches medication or a medical condition, we say clearly that the content is general
		information — <strong>not medical advice</strong> — and encourage readers to speak to their doctor, pharmacist,
		or a registered dietitian about their individual situation. Nutrify AI is a wellness tool, not a medical device.
	</p>

